      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verification demonstrated via benchmark problems with known analytical solutions (Timoshenko beam, Hertzian contact) showing <1% error in relevant QoIs.",
      "rationale": "Benchmark verification cases for beam bending and contact mechanics were executed in Ansys Mechanical 2022 R1. Results agree with analytical solutions to within 0.4% for stiffness and 0.8% for peak stress. Gradation 2 achieved: independent benchmark suite with documented pass/fail criteria."
