      "acceptanceCriteria": "Mesh convergence study demonstrates <2% change in all three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) between medium and fine mesh densities; Richardson extrapolation GCI < 1%.",
      "rationale": "Three mesh densities (coarse ~80k, medium ~320k, fine ~1.28M elements) were evaluated. QoI variation between medium and fine meshes: stiffness 0.9%, yield force 1.1%, force at 40 mm 0.7%. Richardson extrapolation GCI values all below 0.8%. Medium mesh selected for production runs. Gradation 3 achieved: systematic convergence study with extrapolation-based error estimate."
