      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement) are directly linked to the COU decision (structural adequacy of pedicle screw construct) and are the same quantities used in the regulatory submission.",
      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three primary outputs specified in ASTM F1717 and are the quantities cited in the 510(k) predicate comparison. These QoIs directly characterize the structural performance attributes relevant to the COU decision. Gradation 3 achieved."
